summary: Comprehensive testing of French fitness tracking application completed. Backend APIs fully functional (100% success rate), frontend UI working with minor issues in exercise library selectors.

ui_bugs.issue: CSS selector parsing error when trying to select exercise elements programmatically
ui_bugs.impact: Only affects automated testing, not user functionality

design_issues.issue: Missing Description or aria-describedby for accessibility
affected_selectors: DialogContent in workout and nutrition forms

passed_tests: Nutrition tracking with macros and amino acids
Progress overview with workout and nutrition data
AI recommendations correctly blocked for non-premium users
Stripe checkout session creation for monthly/yearly plans
Landing page load with correct branding and navigation
Dashboard navigation between all major sections
Workouts page with exercise library display
Nutrition page with meal logging functionality
Premium page with subscription plans display
Dark theme implementation with orange primary color (#F97316)
French language interface throughout the application

success_percentage.frontend: 95% (minor CSS selector and accessibility issues only)
